    4 HEAD CONSTRUCTION STAGE CS 100 G_K,1
    5 STO#CS_CSM 100    $ use of variable #cs_csm in CTRL ASE TEXT see manual -> CTRL CANT
    6   PAGE UNII 0  ! STANDARD INPUT UNITS
    7   ECHO DISP,FORC,NOST,BEDD,LOAD,REAC,GRP,LSUM NO
    8   CTRL DIFF 1000 $ difference loadcases increment
    9   CTRL CANT   12 $ 1 = with original inclination
