    1 +PROG AQB $ Check print stresses in construction stages
    2 $ Dat : C:\...\Approach_5_(Stahlbau)\Approach5.dat  (#002)          22.10.2025
    3 $ Job : EBWEW1108:000019                                                 10:59
    4 HEAD CHECK PRINT STRESSES IN CONSTRUCTION STAGES
    5 $ Please look for "Analysis of Section - Normal Stresses" in the AQB report
    6 ECHO SECT,COMB,FORC,REIN,STRE,USEP NO
    7 ECHO TABS 1+2 $ 1+2 = print all tendons separately
    8 $ please insert CTRL AQB TEXT 'ECHO TABS 2' $ to only get the sum of all tendons
    9   CTRL SVRF   1.00000 $ take into account reinforcement for C+S
   10   CTRL VM   VAL2 1.0 $ take into account normal force delta-N of torsion in bending design DESI
   11   CTRL WARN 117 $ otherwise warning as no tendons exist in beam elements
   12 $
   13 $ beams to be used:
   14 BEAM     10033 X     0.000[M] CS - $ sections without construction stages
   15 $
   16 $ loadcases to be used:
   17 LC  5??? $ all 5000...GPC-loadcases as in the LC-list in file _csmlf.dat
   18 ECHO FORC YES $ to check the automatic found and applied loadcases -> Considered Load Cases
   19 $
   20 $ Combinations:
   21 $ *************************************************************
   22 $ stresses in single loadcases:
   23 COMB SOLO LC1 5100          TITL "Solo_100 G_k,1          " CST  100
   24 COMB SOLO LC1 5200          TITL "Solo_200 G_k,2          " CST  200
   25 $ *************************************************************
   26 $ stresses in sum of loadcases:
   27 COMB LINE $ ***************** separation line
   28 COMB EXTR LC1  LC2  LC3  LC4  LC5  LC6 LCST=7100 CST=100 TITL="Sum_100 G_k,1           "
   29       SUM 5100
   30 COMB EXTR LC1  LC2  LC3  LC4  LC5  LC6 LCST=7200 CST=200 TITL="Sum_200 G_k,2           "
   31       SUM 5100 5200
   32 COMB GMAX LCST  7999 $ stores extreme values of stresses of all COMB lines.
   33 STRE E $ prints linear stresses of combinations
   34 $ Please look for "Analysis of Section - Normal Stresses" in the AQB report
   35 END
 
